â± JavaScript Stopwatch
A simple, browser-based Stopwatch built using vanilla JavaScript and DOM manipulation.
It allows users to start, stop, and reset the timer with an accurate HH:MM:SS display.

ğŸ“œ Features
Start / Stop / Reset controls

Live updating display in the HH:MM:SS format

Accurate second-by-second tracking

Reusable Stopwatch class with:

Encapsulated elapsed time tracking

Start, stop, and reset methods

Static formatting utilities (formatTime, zeroPadding)

Works entirely in the browser without external libraries

